{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":{"id":"SitePage /posts/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS/"}},"pageContext":{"url":"/posts/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS/","relativePath":"posts/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS.md","relativeDir":"posts","base":"How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS.md","name":"How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS","frontmatter":{"title":"How to edit and save hosts file in Windows 8 OS","stackbit_url_path":"posts/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS","date":"2013-08-06 06:26:36.3544437","excerpt":"","comments_count":0,"positive_reactions_count":0,"tags":["hosts","runas","windows 8"],"canonical_url":"https://be-net.azurewebsites.net/post/2013/08/06/How-to-edit-and-save-hosts-file-in-Windows-8-OS","template":"post"},"html":"<h2><font color=\"#9b00d3\">Problem:</font></h2>  <p>After you edited your hosts file in Windows 8 system and then when you save it the following save as dialog prompted:</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_642.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 54.05405405405405%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/c5f1ef23467485e1dfbd2b3c7b80e33c/fcda8/image_thumb_330.png\" srcset=\"/static/c5f1ef23467485e1dfbd2b3c7b80e33c/12f09/image_thumb_330.png 148w,\n/static/c5f1ef23467485e1dfbd2b3c7b80e33c/e4a3f/image_thumb_330.png 295w,\n/static/c5f1ef23467485e1dfbd2b3c7b80e33c/fcda8/image_thumb_330.png 590w,\n/static/c5f1ef23467485e1dfbd2b3c7b80e33c/6db71/image_thumb_330.png 659w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>If you click “Save” button, the following alert message popped out, claiming that you don’t have sufficient permission.</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_643.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.4054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/3cd8ac56fcc9fc5bff1d660692db5666/fcda8/image_thumb_331.png\" srcset=\"/static/3cd8ac56fcc9fc5bff1d660692db5666/12f09/image_thumb_331.png 148w,\n/static/3cd8ac56fcc9fc5bff1d660692db5666/e4a3f/image_thumb_331.png 295w,\n/static/3cd8ac56fcc9fc5bff1d660692db5666/fcda8/image_thumb_331.png 590w,\n/static/3cd8ac56fcc9fc5bff1d660692db5666/6db71/image_thumb_331.png 659w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>You are logged on the system as system administrator, and you checked the hosts file properties, it shows that administrator has full control on it, but why the system doesn’t allow you to save it?!</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_644.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100.67567567567568%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/3751bcc2366e2fa707d8400c11ff8049/fcda8/image_thumb_332.png\" srcset=\"/static/3751bcc2366e2fa707d8400c11ff8049/12f09/image_thumb_332.png 148w,\n/static/3751bcc2366e2fa707d8400c11ff8049/e4a3f/image_thumb_332.png 295w,\n/static/3751bcc2366e2fa707d8400c11ff8049/fcda8/image_thumb_332.png 590w,\n/static/3751bcc2366e2fa707d8400c11ff8049/6db71/image_thumb_332.png 659w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <h2><font color=\"#9b00d3\">Cause:</font></h2>  <p>Although you are logged in to the system as administrator, but when you open a file, the file would be opened as a normal user privilege by default.</p>  <h2><font color=\"#9b00d3\">Solution:</font></h2>  <p>To edit the hosts file and save it, you can follow these steps:</p>  <ol>   <li>In the metro UI, type “cmd”, and then right click on the “Command Prompt”<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_645.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 82.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/8e144621ff5095ff32f5fd99ae24d64f/fcda8/image_thumb_333.png\" srcset=\"/static/8e144621ff5095ff32f5fd99ae24d64f/12f09/image_thumb_333.png 148w,\n/static/8e144621ff5095ff32f5fd99ae24d64f/e4a3f/image_thumb_333.png 295w,\n/static/8e144621ff5095ff32f5fd99ae24d64f/fcda8/image_thumb_333.png 590w,\n/static/8e144621ff5095ff32f5fd99ae24d64f/80d71/image_thumb_333.png 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></li>    <li>Click “Run as administrator”, then change to the directory to the hosts file in by typing “cd C:\\Windows\\System32\\Drivers\\etc” in the cmd line </li>    <li>Then type “notepad hosts”<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_646.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/795c5c48f02f91b6679d5a1989c7a079/fcda8/image_thumb_334.png\" srcset=\"/static/795c5c48f02f91b6679d5a1989c7a079/12f09/image_thumb_334.png 148w,\n/static/795c5c48f02f91b6679d5a1989c7a079/e4a3f/image_thumb_334.png 295w,\n/static/795c5c48f02f91b6679d5a1989c7a079/fcda8/image_thumb_334.png 590w,\n/static/795c5c48f02f91b6679d5a1989c7a079/80d71/image_thumb_334.png 625w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></li>    <li>Now you can edit the hosts file and save it without problem.</li> </ol>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label":"Twitter","url":"https://twitter.com/zizhujy","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-twitter","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jefftian5","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-instagram","new_window":true,"type":"actio